Therefore, the main language in scientific literature of this field was German at the time, thus, limiting the accessibility to the publications and scientific discussions from back then for the broader English-speaking scientific community today. Purpose Here, an annotated translation of Meissner's first description of the submucosal plexus is provided along with a short biography of Georg Meissner and a review of the scientific literature and controversy surrounding his discovery.
